This paper is about developing a model for task-oriented dialog systems using recurrent neural networks. The paper focuses on the use of supervised and reinforcement learning to optimize the model. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SD (Software Engineering), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), as the paper also touches on topics related to software development, user interaction, and machine learning.
